main.name: HCONRES81
main.longTitle: CONCURRENT RESOLUTION Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 1158.
main.enactingFormula: Resolved by the House of Representatives (the Senate concurring),

section.content: That, in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 1158, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall make the following correction: Amend the long title so as to read: “Making consolidated appropriations for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2020, and for other purposes.”.

signature.role: Clerk of the House of Representatives.
